organic.title: Camp Leo for Children with Diabetes
organic.snippet: Camp Leo is dedicated to enriching the lives of those affected by Type 1 Diabetes through programs that inspire, empower, educate, and promote community.

organic.title: Elementary School Camp - Camp Leo for Children with Diabetes
organic.snippet: This camp session is designed for campers going into grades 3-6 in the Fall. Historically Elementary camp is designed for campers entering 3rd-5th grade.

organic.title: High School Camp — Camp Leo for Children with Diabetes
organic.snippet: Our traditional overnight resident High School Camp is built for teens with diabetes, offering campers more options and choices in activities and autonomy.

organic.title: About Camp Leo
organic.snippet: Camp Leo offers the ONLY overnight camp in Western Washington exclusively dedicated to children with Type 1 Diabetes.
